iana.encoding_considerations:
Security considerations: The GPXsee online map definition file 
   defines the URL and parameters of online maps loaded by GPXSee  
   (and possibly other applications). The content is not 
   interpreted/executed, but the defined URL will be accessed. 
   Additionally, the parameters/URL may include secrets like 
   username/password or some kind of service access codes. In such 
   case, privacy or integrity services must be provided externally.

Interoperability considerations: None.
